extendedInfo.description: Do the 92 is the application for football fans to show just how committed to the cause they really are.Available on Android devices, Do the 92 allows groundhoppers to keep track of the Premier and Football League clubs they've visited up and down England, from Carlisle to Portsmouth and everywhere in between.As well as staying on top of your stadium ticklist, the app also provides handy information on each ground, all in one place.Collect trophies as you go and advance from armchair fan to legendary fan status. Share your achievements with friends and rediscover your old stamping grounds through the map feature.Can you Do the 92?Football # Stadiums # Grounds # Map # Soccer # England # Clubs # Premier League # Championship # League 1 # League 2
